{"type": "article", "id": 10066, "title": "Adidas 新战靴", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-27T07:37:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052354526Q3ibxsw2KVntR9l.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAdidas 最近推出了两款新的战靴，分别是适合控制性球员的 ACE15 和适合速度型球员的 X15。前者采用由工程 3D 材质打造的新材料鞋面，并且采用全新的大底设计。后者以轻巧和贴合取胜。同时，随着这两款球鞋的发布，Adidas 宣布淘汰了 猎鹰，F50，11pro，狂战士这四个系列。目前，两款鞋子价格售价 1499 元，已经开始预售，将于 7 月 1 日发货。这是<a href=\"http://adidas.tmall.com/p/football2015.htm#x\" target=\"_blank\">天猫购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235448fHgNAXJuOBFrxbCm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.01222494\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354491oT9F6GV3S7na0jl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354494Ed8p0wXn7AtxIs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235450jyXxowcVOtrYvnER.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354502abCKcyRituMF7ZT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235450e57zOJXIMRqEFAfs.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235451NskCpa6zjIfd9JyQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354514cpdguOW5Q8EblFi.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}